      <title>鲍威尔：美联储政策将“随着时间的推移”转向中性立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/powell-fed-policy-to-move-to-neutral-stance-over-time-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，央行将“逐步”降低利率，整体经济“状况良好”。他在纳什维尔举行的全国商业经济协会年会上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/powell-fed-policy-to-move-to-neutral-stance-over-time-video</guid>
