    <item>
      <title>道明银行在美国扩大调查后解决国债欺诈案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/td-bank-resolves-treasuries-spoofing-case-amid-wider-us-probes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行 (Toronto-Dominion Bank) 将支付超过 2000 万美元，作为与美国检察官和监管机构达成协议的一部分，以解决对一名前交易员涉嫌下达“欺骗”订单以操纵美国国债市场的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/td-bank-resolves-treasuries-spoofing-case-amid-wider-us-probes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
